});
```

**Next.js (`tsconfig.json`):**
```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "paths": {
      "@/*": ["./src/*"]
    }
  }
}
```

## Barrel Export Patterns

### Atom Level Barrel Export

```typescript
// src/components/atoms/index.ts
